    mmc: tmio: support caps2 flags
    
    Allow tmio mmc glue drivers to pass mmc_host::caps2 flags down to
    the mmc layer.
    
    Signed-off-by: Guennadi Liakhovetski <g.liakhovetski@gmx.de>
    Signed-off-by: Chris Ball <cjb@laptop.org>

